name: FarmSoundsforSleep
0:
”Alexa open farm sounds”
”Alexa ask farm sounds to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: farm sounds
des: Listening to natural sounds of a farm is the perfect way to get ready for bed. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Farm Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
